                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17880109-23-off113 t17880109-23-cd114"></join>, three linen shirts, value 5 s. a muslin handkerchief, value 1 s. three aprons, value 18 d. a pair of ruffles, value 6 d. two shifts, value 18 d. four muslin caps, value 1 s. twelve linen caps, value 2 s. seven linen handkerchiefs, value 4 s. and a piece of linen, value 2 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t17880109-23-victim242" type="victimName">
